-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Tahir: IOCs’ Divestment ‘ll Impact Competitiveness, Investments in Nigeria’s Oil Industry" href="../../../2024/03/25/tahir-iocs-divestment-ll-impact-competitiveness-investments-in-nigerias-oil-industry5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/0-1-271.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Tahir: IOCs’ Divestment ‘ll Impact Competitiveness, Investments in Nigeria’s Oil Industry" href="../../../2024/03/25/tahir-iocs-divestment-ll-impact-competitiveness-investments-in-nigerias-oil-industry5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Tahir: IOCs’ Divestment ‘ll Impact Competitiveness, Investments in Nigeria’s Oil Industry</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Echoes from Nigeria’s Aggressive Monetary Policy Tightening" href="../../../2024/03/25/echoes-from-nigerias-aggressive-monetary-policy-tightening5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/0-751.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Echoes from Nigeria’s Aggressive Monetary Policy Tightening" href="../../../2024/03/25/echoes-from-nigerias-aggressive-monetary-policy-tightening5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Echoes from Nigeria’s Aggressive Monetary Policy Tightening</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="CPS: PenCom Empowers Employees to Report Non-compliance" href="../../../2024/03/25/cps-pencom-empowers-employees-to-report-non-compliance5593.html?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/PenCom-1-800x450.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="CPS: PenCom Empowers Employees to Report Non-compliance" href="../../../2024/03/25/cps-pencom-empowers-employees-to-report-non-compliance5593.html?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">CPS: PenCom Empowers Employees to Report Non-compliance</h3></a></div></article></div><div class="jsx-cf68f6ec6f012ae8 item"><article class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de container vertical-slider-container medium"><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de thumbnail"><a title="Export: Shippers Express Concerns over Inconsistent Exchange Rate" href="../../../2024/03/25/export-shippers-express-concerns-over-inconsistent-exchange-rate5593?amp=1"><amp-img width="150" height="150" layout="fill" object-fit="cover" src="../../../../../global.ariseplay.com/amg/www.thisdaylive.com/uploads/Exchange-rate-definition-800x450.jpg" class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de i-amphtml-layout-fill i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" i-amphtml-layout="fill"></amp-img></a></div><div class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-text"><a title="Export: Shippers Express Concerns over Inconsistent Exchange Rate" href="../../../2024/03/25/export-shippers-express-concerns-over-inconsistent-exchange-rate5593?amp=1"><h3 class="jsx-5544b3734f8a66de article-title">Export: Shippers Express Concerns over Inconsistent Exchange Rate</h3></a></div></article></div><div